    "headline": "MarketAxess (NASDAQ:MKTX) Beats Q1 CY2026 Sales Expectations",
    "summary": "Electronic bond trading platform MarketAxess (NASDAQ:MKTX) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 11.9% year on year to $233.4 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.25 per share was 4.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
